===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# A [[vessel]] of wood or tin, etc., usually cylindrical and having a [[handle]] -- used esp. for carrying liquids, as water or milk, etc.; a [[bucket]] ''(sometimes with a cover)''.
#: The milkmaid carried a '''pail''' of milk in each hand.
# A company of [[wasp]]s.

